                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This is my brother's ticket, which was tied to the stick—it is my writing.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I know nothing at all about it—I saw people run<lb></lb>ning—some man stopped me—I was going to meet a friend.</p>
